data.description:
Affordable Housing In Asheville, on a Half Acre Lot, with an Attached Garage! This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home also has an Unheated Large Bonus Room. 
The HVAC Is Only 7 Months Old, and the Roof Is Only 9 Years Old. Great Location, Just Minutes from Patton Avenue and Downtown Asheville. Feels 
Very Private In this Established Neighborhood, But NO HOA. Back of Property Slopes Down to a Small Creek.
PLEASE NO DRIVEBYS - All Showings Accompanied By An Agent.
